            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What&#x27;s New</h2>
<ul>
  <li>add read-only Mac App Store support</li>
  <li>add Homebrew services manager UI</li>
  <li>add advanced package actions: reinstall, fetch, link, unlink</li>
  <li>add saved package groups/watchlists</li>
  <li>add command history and retry for package actions</li>
  <li>add dry-run previews for cleanup and autoremove</li>
  <li>add homepage button to Discover detail view</li>
</ul>]]></description>
